<plot>'TRAVELLING LIGHT: Artists on the Move' follows 5 nomadic artists on their quest to live life as an art form. Filmed in 11 countries, this road-documentary explores the relationship between creativity and travel. Crossing borders of all types, our roaming protagonists take on the world, providing tonic insight into contemporary life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?616766</url></doc>
